00:45.138 --> 00:48.642
which in this case is sort of hurtful.

00:48.702 --> 00:56.771
You also want the regions of interest where there is nothing because that helps you avoid false positives in other frames.

00:57.191 --> 00:59.093
That's why the orange line is below the green line.

00:59.113 --> 01:08.644
But strangely here, in the high confidence regime, you can see that the single frame model has fewer false positives than the context RCNN.

01:08.684 --> 01:12.748
